Description: AI-assisted malware reverse-engineering debugger
 AIDebug performs malware triage and reverse-engineering support for PE and
 ELF binaries. It extracts function-level behavior, maps suspicious logic to
 MITRE ATT&CK, and emits detection-oriented outputs such as YARA candidates,
 IOC lists, JSON exports, and HTML analyst reports.
 .
 Static analysis can run without executing samples. Optional Anthropic-backed
 analysis and Frida-based dynamic tracing depend on Python modules that may
 need separate Kali/Debian packaging.
